overview.en: PEC(Photoelectricitychain) is initiated by Singapore photoelectric energy foundation.PEC block chain technology luminous energy generation service system.In order to solve some outstanding problems of the Photoelectricitychain in the actual use scenario.
overview.zh: PEC光电链（PhotoelectricityChain）是由新加坡光电能源基金会发起，光电链是一个基于区块链技术的光能发电服务系统，为解决光电区块链在实际使用场景下的一些突出问题。
